txt.en: 'Most of a town is made of wood...it is a quick material to build with and makes strong structures. We have to be watchful for fire, but if we built with stone, it would be ten years before we finished. In order to get the wood we need cut into boards, we need to repair the Lumber-mill.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
